sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant MainAgent as Main Agent<br/>（Window）
    participant Mailbox
    participant Teammate as Teammate<br/>（InProcess/Remote）
    User->>MainAgent: 启动 Swarm
    MainAgent->>Teammate: spawnMultiAgent()
    Teammate->>Teammate: 执行，需要权限
    Teammate->>Mailbox: 发送权限请求
    Mailbox->>MainAgent: 转发请求
    MainAgent->>User: 显示权限对话框
    User->>MainAgent: 批准/拒绝
    MainAgent->>Mailbox: 权限决策
    Mailbox->>Teammate: 转发决策
    Teammate->>Teammate: 继续执行或中止
    Teammate->>MainAgent: 返回结果
